ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Russia) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the SPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES (RUSSIA) REGULATIONS in order to add four individuals and five entities to Schedule 1, add 1 entity to Schedule 2 and shorten the period of maturity for loans, bonds or debentures under subsection 3.1 (1) and remove two entities from the list of designated persons in Schedule 1 of the Russia Regulations.
